76561197993500303,Recommended,274480,18103277,"Posted: 19 September, 2015",all,Gorebane,"A very fun Diablo-esque space RPG.You create your ship, then progress through the dynamically created levels gaining levels and items as you go. Once you meet one of the winning/losing criteria of the system, then you create a new system to explore.When creating a new system you can set the base level of the enemies in it, as such you can to an extent set your own difficulty level. Additionally you can set the size of the system, number of races etc as you can in many other games.If you're looking for a simple, but addictive, space RPG this is it."
