,Not Recommended,274480,13574274,"Posted: 24 December, 2014",all,CryonicSuspension,"I wish that I had played the demo first; I found this game disappointing.Based on online, gaming magazine reviews and Youtube reviews, I was expecting something similar to Space Rangers 2: Reboot or a 4 x game like either Star Control or Master of Orion 2. This game is neither of these things.You are the last of the Drox race, a once mighty Empire that was all but destroyed in a war. You only have one ship, you don't build more and you don't colonize planets. Your goal is to figure out which AI race will emerge as the strongest race and brown-nose them, by doing quests for them. A race might ask you to find a replacement power supply for a planet or smuggle in hand-held weapons, to quell subsequent riots. It sounds more interesting than it actually is, since it is just a case of buying an item from a specific vendor and then transporting it to the specific planet.Figuring out which race will emerge victorious is not difficult, since you have 100% intelligence gathering, regarding Empire strength. Some races lack social skills, or are fickle, or aggressive. I knew how the second game would play out, after losing the first. The race traits don't change between games, so that will completely kill any longevity.You spend most of your time flying around, at the speed of a snail, exploring derelict ships, in an attempt to uncover the fog of war. Random ships and races will attack you. Combat consists of spamming the 1 key because the other two weapons in the game are worthless, by comparison. Finding random loot and juggling items was fun in the first game but you figure out how to min / max the game in a couple of hours.This game was a waste of time and money, to the point that I highly recommend playing the demo or avoiding it altogether. I wish that I could get my money back. Play whatever is the best Space Rangers game out there.Master of Orion 2 is still the best 4x game ever:http://www.gog.com/game/master_of_orion_1_2Alpha Centauri is also an excellent 4x game:http://www.gog.com/game/sid_meiers_alpha_centauri"
